Messages.Value: Thank you for calling the travel agency, my name is Elijah. How can I assist you today?
Hi Elijah, my name is Sarah Thompson. I have a question about my upcoming trip to New York City.
Of course Sarah, I'd be happy to help. What's the question you have?
I booked my flight through American Airlines and I'm having some trouble. My flight was delayed and I was wondering if I'm entitled to any kind of compensation.
I'm sorry to hear that Sarah. Can you please provide me with your flight details so I can look into this for you?
Yes, it was American Airlines Flight 123 departing from Los Angeles at 4pm on May 15th.

Thank you, let me check for you. Yes, it looks like there was a delay of 2 hours for your flight. According to the American Airlines compensation policy, passengers are entitled to a travel voucher for future flights.
Thank you Elijah, that's helpful. Do you have any other recommendations regarding flights to New York City?
Certainly Sarah, we have many options available. Do you have any preferences regarding airline or flight times?
Not really, I just want to make sure I get a good deal.
I can definitely help you with that. Let me check some flight options for you and see what I can find.
Thank you so much Elijah, I really appreciate your help.
It was my pleasure Sarah, I'm glad I could assist you. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you again for your help Elijah.
You're welcome Sarah, have a great day!
